Business Performance Report Dashboard (Power BI Project)
Project Overview
This project is an interactive Power BI dashboard developed to analyze overall business performance using sales, customer, and operational metrics. The dashboard transforms raw business data into actionable insights through interactive visualizations, KPI monitoring, and trend analysis.
The project demonstrates practical business intelligence and data analytics capabilities including:
•	Data cleaning and transformation
•	Data modeling and relationships
•	KPI creation using DAX
•	Interactive dashboard development
•	Performance and trend analysis
•	Business insight generation
•	Executive reporting and visualization
________________________________________
Objective
The primary objective of this project is to:
•	Monitor overall business performance using key metrics
•	Analyze sales and operational trends
•	Identify top-performing categories and segments
•	Track profitability and growth patterns
•	Build an interactive dashboard for data-driven decision-making
________________________________________
Dashboard Overview
The Power BI dashboard provides a centralized reporting solution for analyzing business performance across multiple dimensions.
Dashboard Features
•	KPI summary cards
