Data Cleaning & Preparation
Several preprocessing and transformation steps were completed before dashboard development.
Data Cleaning Activities
•	Removed duplicate and inconsistent records
•	Standardized column formats
•	Converted data types for accurate calculations
•	Handled missing and null values
•	Structured date fields for time intelligence analysis
Data Modeling
•	Built relationships between fact and dimension tables
•	Created a dedicated calendar/date table
•	Established star-schema style modeling where applicable
•	Optimized model for reporting efficiency
