Key Insights
Business Performance Insights
•	Certain categories or segments contribute disproportionately to revenue.
•	Sales and profit trends reveal seasonal and operational patterns.
•	Business growth varies across customer or product segments.
•	High-performing areas can be identified through KPI comparisons.
Operational Insights
•	Profitability does not always align with sales volume.
•	Some segments may generate strong revenue but lower margins.
•	Trend analysis helps identify performance fluctuations and business opportunities.
