Recommendations
Revenue Optimization
•	Focus investment on high-performing products or segments.
•	Improve sales strategies for underperforming categories.
•	Monitor seasonal trends for targeted campaigns.
Profitability Improvements
•	Analyze low-margin areas for cost optimization.
•	Prioritize profitable customer and product segments.
•	Use KPI tracking for continuous performance monitoring.
Business Intelligence Enhancements
•	Integrate real-time data refresh processes.
•	Add predictive analytics and forecasting models.
•	Expand dashboard with customer retention and operational metrics.
